nhc_headline: ...GABRIELLE MOVING NORTHEASTWARD INTO THE OPEN CENTRAL ATLANTIC... ...INTERESTS IN THE AZORES SHOULD MONITOR ITS PROGRESS...
summary: ...GABRIELLE MOVING NORTHEASTWARD INTO THE OPEN CENTRAL ATLANTIC... ...INTERESTS IN THE AZORES SHOULD MONITOR ITS PROGRESS... As of 5:00 AM AST Tue Sep 23 the center of Gabrielle was located near 33.2, -59.7 with movement NE at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 949 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 140 mph.
